high_descs: Move forward and go to the counter, adjacent to the fridge.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn to your left and move forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the apple inside and chill it, then take it out.
Turn around and go to the sink, then look up to the microwave above it.
Put the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step to your left then walk until you're almost at the sink but turn left before you get to it and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the apple that's in front of you near the wall.
Take two steps to your left to face the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the stove then turn right and walk to the sink.
Look up above the sink at the microwave then open the door and put the apple in there before closing the door again.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter on the left of the stove.
Grab an apple from the counter.
Go to the fridge on the left.
Put the apple in the fridge, then take it out.
Walk to the sink behind you.
Put the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Chill an apple and heat it.
